The A.L.E. LIVE at Brunch
Sunday, June 8, 2025
12:00 PM
3:00 PM
Google Calendar
ICS
The A.L.E. (The Anders/Lambert Experience) is the dynamic duo of Zach Lambert and Jen Anders, two passionate singer-songwriters and guitarists blending country, blues, Americana, classic rock, and pop into a soulful, feel-good experience. Influenced by artists like Brandi Carlile, Tyler Childers, Bill Withers, and Koko Taylor, they bring raw emotion, tight harmonies, and a love for storytelling to every performance.
Whether playing breweries, beach bars, city events, or theme parks, The A.L.E. creates an inviting, high-energy atmosphere that keeps audiences engaged. Performing a mix of originals and unique covers they play the songs you know and love with a unique sound.
If you’re looking for nature-loving music makers who bring heart and authenticity to every song, The A.L.E. is the experience you don’t want to miss.
Open 11am - 3pm
$25 bottomless mimosas all day!
